\end{document} percentiles. We used a two-tailed Mann–Whitney U test for all statistical tests. For the box plots, the central mark is the median, the edges of the box are the 25th and 75th percentiles (interquartile range), the whiskers correspond to the range \documentclass{aastex}\usepackage{amsbsy}\usepackage{amsfonts}\usepackage{amssymb}\usepackage{bm}\usepackage{mathrsfs}\usepackage{pifont}\usepackage{stmaryrd}\usepackage{textcomp}\usepackage{portland, xspace}\usepackage{amsmath, amsxtra}\usepackage{upgreek}\pagestyle{empty}\DeclareMathSizes{10}{9}{7}{6}\begin{document}
